data.description: NEW CARPET, APPLIANCES & PAINT!!! Spacious 2-story home available in Elm Creek! 4 bed, 2.5 bath featuring a light & airy open floor plan. Kitchen with a center island, gas range, pantry & breakfast area. Living room with formal dining area on main floor. Extra flex space downstairs to serve as an office. The primary bedroom has ample space with his-and-hers closets~ The en-suite primary bath features a double vanity, garden tub, & separate shower. Enjoy your Private backyard which is HUGE!! Great location! Easy access to 290. Just 30 minutes from Downtown Austin, Austin Bergstrom Airport and Tesla. Convenient to Super Walmart and HEB.
